  "text": "Setting. The size of the queue in each sensor node is set to be = 60, an appropriate value to produce a preferable AR model for environment monitoring [CITATION_1] . For the monitoring algorithm of local AR model, we adopt similar parameters setting as PAQ [CITATION_2] ; that is, = 0.03, Λ = 15, and ] = 8. We also adopt the optimum parameters setting for the compared algorithms. Specifically, trend similarity threshold = 80% and = 3 ℎ for EEDC. Regarding to ELink and ELink, we set weight vector ⃗ = (0.5, 0.3, 0.2) for the coefficients of AR(3) model and fix the feature distance threshold = 0.5. All results in this section are the average values of 10 simulations.",
